---
title: Brioche Shrimp Rolls with Arugula Radish Salad
description: Is it possible for a sandwich to taste like the beach? Because this Maine-inspired meal with buttery brioche, juicy shrimp, and creamy tarragon dressing has summer written all over it. Feel free to grab a fruity drink (preferably with a mini umbrella) and dig your toes into the imaginary sand while feasting on our refreshing seafood dinner.
